entry.value: SELECT CRASH_RECORD_ID, POSTED_SPEED_LIMIT, WEATHER_CONDITION, LIGHTING_CONDITION, ROADWAY_SURFACE_COND, CRASH_TYPE, NUM_UNITS, MOST_SEVERE_INJURY, INJURIES_TOTAL, LATITUDE, LONGITUDE, "Boundaries - ZIP Codes" as District_by_zip, CAST(SUBSTRING(CRASH_DATE, 4, 2) AS INT) AS "Day", CAST(SUBSTRING(CRASH_DATE, 1, 2) AS INT) AS "Month", CAST(SUBSTRING(CRASH_DATE, 7, 4) AS INT) AS "Year" FROM FLOWFILE WHERE CAST(SUBSTRING(CRASH_DATE, 7, 4) AS INT) >= 2015

SELECT ID, "Primary Type" as Primary_Type, Description, Latitude, Longitude, Arrest, Domestic, "Boundaries - ZIP Codes" as District_by_zip, CAST(SUBSTRING("Date", 4, 2) AS INT) AS "Day", CAST(SUBSTRING("Date", 1, 2) AS INT) AS "Month", CAST(SUBSTRING("Date", 7, 4) AS INT) AS "Year" FROM FLOWFILE WHERE CAST(SUBSTRING("Date", 7, 4) AS INT) >= 2015
